query:
SELECT
                COUNT(*) AS "count: _"
            FROM
                conversation_messages
            WHERE
                conversation_id = ?1
                AND sender_as_client_uuid IS NOT NULL
                AND sender_as_domain IS NOT NULL
                AND timestamp >
                (
                    SELECT
                        last_read
                    FROM
                        conversations
                    WHERE
                        conversation_id = ?1
                )
